# OWID RAG 규칙

- 엔진: [owid_enhanced_rag.py](mdc:app/services/tools/owid_enhanced_rag.py), 래퍼: [owid_rag_tool.py](mdc:app/services/tools/owid_rag_tool.py)
- 임베딩: `intfloat/multilingual-e5-base`, 리랭커: `cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2`
